comments:
Created 1.4.1954 out of the parishes of Blenheim Park and Hessington 
    Without. See also Table 2, note (f).

Abolished 1.4.1954 and added to the parish of Blenheim. See 
    also Table 2, notes (d) and (f).

Created 1.4.1949 from the parishes of Wychwood and Cornbury Park. 
    See also Table 2, note (f).

Abolished 1.4.1949 and added to the parish of Cornbury & 
    Wychwood.
Abolished 1.4.1932 and added to the parish of Rollright.

Abolished 1.4.1974 and added to the parish of Woodstock. 
    See also Table 2, notes (d) and (f).

Abolished 1.4.1932 and added to the parish of Shipton under 
    Wychwood.

Transferred from Gloucestershire to Warwickshire on 20.10.1844. 
    See also Table 2, note (b).
Abolished 1.4.1932 and added to the parish of Rollright.

Abolished 1.4.1974 and added to the parish of Woodstock. 
    See also Table 2, notes (d) and (f).

Created 1.4.1932 from the parishes of Great Rollright and Little 
    Rollright. See also Table 2, note (f).
Abolished 25.12.1868 to become part of the parish of Chilson.

Created 1.8.1857 out of the parishes of Ascot under Wychwood, 
    Chilson and Leafield. Abolished 1.4.1949 and divided between the parishes of Cornbury 
    & Wychwood and Leafield.
